statements: SELECT * FROM parking_data WHERE parking_status = 'occupied';
SELECT parking_id, car_plate_number, check_out_time FROM parking_data WHERE parking_location = 'Garage A' AND check_out_time IS NULL;
SELECT parking_id, parking_location, car_plate_number, check_in_time FROM parking_data ORDER BY check_in_time DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT parking_location FROM parking_data;
SELECT * FROM parking_data WHERE check_out_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM parking_data WHERE parking_status = 'occupied';
SELECT parking_location, car_plate_number FROM parking_data WHERE check_out_time IS NULL ORDER BY check_in_time DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT parking_location FROM parking_data WHERE check_out_time IS NOT NULL;
SELECT car_plate_number FROM parking_data WHERE parking_status = 'reserved' AND check_in_time < '2022-01-01';
SELECT parking_status, COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM parking_data GROUP BY parking_status HAVING total_count > 1 ORDER BY total_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM parking_lots
SELECT parking_lot_name, total_spaces FROM parking_lots
SELECT parking_lot_id, available_spaces FROM parking_lots
SELECT * FROM parking_log
SELECT entry_time, exit_time FROM parking_log
SELECT parking_lot_id, parking_lot_name FROM parking_lots WHERE total_spaces > 50 ORDER BY parking_lot_name ASC
SELECT * FROM parking_lots WHERE available_spaces < 10 ORDER BY total_spaces DESC
SELECT parking_lot_id, parking_lot_name, total_spaces, available_spaces FROM parking_lots WHERE total_spaces > available_spaces
SELECT * FROM parking_lots WHERE parking_lot_name ILIKE '%park%'

SELECT pl.parking_lot_id, pl.parking_lot_name, count(pl.parking_lot_id) AS total_logs FROM parking_lots pl JOIN parking_log plg ON pl.parking_lot_id = plg.parking_lot_id GROUP BY pl.parking_lot_id, pl.parking_lot_name ORDER BY total_logs DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM parking_zones;
SELECT zone_id, zone_name FROM parking_zones WHERE city_id = 1;
SELECT zone_name, total_spaces FROM parking_zones ORDER BY total_spaces DESC;
SELECT zone_name, city_id FROM parking_zones WHERE total_spaces > 50;
SELECT * FROM parking_spots WHERE occupied = true;
SELECT * FROM parking_zones ORDER BY zone_name DESC, city_id ASC
SELECT zone_name, total_spaces FROM parking_zones WHERE city_id = 1 ORDER BY total_spaces DESC
SELECT zone_name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_spots FROM parking_zones JOIN parking_spots ON parking_zones.zone_id = parking_spots.zone_id GROUP BY zone_name

SELECT zone_name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_entries FROM parking_zones JOIN parking_spots ON parking_zones.zone_id = parking_spots.zone_id JOIN parking_history ON parking_spots.spot_id = parking_history.spot_id WHERE entry_time > '2022-01-01' GROUP BY zone_name

SELECT zone_name, SUM(total_spaces) AS total_spaces_available FROM parking_zones LEFT JOIN parking_spots ON parking_zones.zone_id = parking_spots.zone_id WHERE occupied = false GROUP BY zone_name ORDER BY total_spaces_available DESC
SELECT * FROM parking_lots;
SELECT lot_name, location FROM parking_lots ORDER BY location ASC;
SELECT lot_id, total_spaces, available_spaces FROM parking_lots WHERE total_spaces > available_spaces;
SELECT sensor_id, sensor_type, status FROM parking_sensors WHERE status = 'active';
SELECT date, total_visits, revenue FROM parking_statistics ORDER BY total_visits DESC, revenue DESC;
SELECT lot_name, location, available_spaces FROM parking_lots WHERE total_spaces > 50
SELECT sensor_id, sensor_type, status FROM parking_sensors WHERE floor = 2 ORDER BY sensor_id DESC
SELECT transaction_id, timestamp, vehicle_plate, payment_amount FROM parking_transactions WHERE payment_amount > 20 ORDER BY timestamp ASC
SELECT lot_name, location, total_spaces, available_spaces FROM parking_lots WHERE available_spaces < total_spaces
SELECT stat_id, lot_id, date, total_visits, revenue FROM parking_statistics WHERE total_visits > 100 ORDER BY revenue DESC
SELECT * FROM parking_lots;
SELECT lot_id, location, capacity FROM parking_lots WHERE status = 'Available';
SELECT user_id, name, email FROM users ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT event_id, vehicle_id, lot_id, enter_time, exit_time FROM parking_events WHERE exit_time IS NULL;
SELECT vehicle_id, license_plate, vehicle_type FROM vehicles WHERE vehicle_type = 'Car';
SELECT * FROM parking_lots WHERE status = 'Open';
SELECT lot_id, location, capacity FROM parking_lots ORDER BY capacity DESC;

SELECT users.name, parking_lots.location, parking_events.enter_time FROM users JOIN vehicles ON users.user_id = vehicles.user_id JOIN parking_events ON vehicles.vehicle_id = parking_events.vehicle_id JOIN parking_lots ON parking_events.lot_id = parking_lots.lot_id;
SELECT vehicle_id, license_plate, vehicle_type FROM vehicles WHERE user_id = 12345;
SELECT event_id, lot_id, enter_time, exit_time FROM parking_events WHERE exit_time IS NULL;
